### Cas 02 — ROR, Règle #1 : requêtes manuelles (format REST Client / JetBrains HTTP Client)
### Prérequis : docker compose up -d (HAPI FHIR sur le port 8080)
### Jouer les blocs dans l'ordre, un par un (Ctrl+Alt+R / clic sur "Send Request" selon le client).

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/fhir

### 1. Vérifier que HAPI FHIR est démarré
GET {{baseUrl}}/metadata

### 2. Charger la Library (CQL encodé en base64)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/Library/OrganizationNomUrgence
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Library",
  "id": "OrganizationNomUrgence",
  "url": "https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/test-cql/Library/OrganizationNomUrgence",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "name": "OrganizationNomUrgence",
  "title": "Organization avec le nom Urgence — Règle #1 ROR",
  "description": "Bibliothèque CQL — cas 02 (ROR) : identifie les Organization qui, ayant un HealthcareService avec une activité opérationnelle 157 ou 249 et un mode de prise en charge 33, n'ont pas \"urgence\" dans leur nom.",
  "status": "active",
  "experimental": true,
  "type": {
    "coding": [
      { "code": "logic-library", "system": "http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/library-type" }
    ]
  },
  "content": [
    {
      "contentType": "text/cql",
      "data": ""
    }
  ]
}

### 3. Charger la Measure (subjectType = Organization)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/Measure/OrganizationsNonConformesNomUrgence
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Measure",
  "id": "OrganizationsNonConformesNomUrgence",
  "url": "https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/test-cql/Measure/OrganizationsNonConformesNomUrgence",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "name": "OrganizationsNonConformesNomUrgence",
  "title": "Organization non conformes à la règle du nom Urgence",
  "status": "active",
  "subjectCodeableConcept": {
    "coding": [{ "code": "Organization", "system": "http://hl7.org/fhir/resource-types" }]
  },
  "library": ["https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/fhir/test-cql/Library/OrganizationNomUrgence"],
  "scoring": {
    "coding": [{ "code": "proportion", "system": "http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/measure-scoring" }]
  },
  "group": [
    {
      "id": "nom-urgence",
      "population": [
        {
          "id": "initial-population",
          "code": { "coding": [{ "code": "initial-population", "system": "http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/measure-population" }] },
          "criteria": { "language": "text/cql-identifier", "expression": "InitialPopulation" }
        },
        {
          "id": "denominator",
          "code": { "coding": [{ "code": "denominator", "system": "http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/measure-population" }] },
          "criteria": { "language": "text/cql-identifier", "expression": "Denominator" }
        },
        {
          "id": "numerator",
          "code": { "coding": [{ "code": "numerator", "system": "http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/measure-population" }] },
          "criteria": { "language": "text/cql-identifier", "expression": "Numerator" }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}

### 4a. Charger Organization org-ch-exemple (non conforme attendue)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/Organization/org-ch-exemple
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Organization",
  "id": "org-ch-exemple",
  "active": true,
  "name": "CH Exemple"
}

### 4b. Charger Organization org-service-urgences (conforme attendue)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/Organization/org-service-urgences
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Organization",
  "id": "org-service-urgences",
  "active": true,
  "name": "Service des Urgences du CH Exemple"
}

### 4c. Charger Organization org-clinique-exemple (non conforme attendue)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/Organization/org-clinique-exemple
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Organization",
  "id": "org-clinique-exemple",
  "active": true,
  "name": "Clinique Exemple"
}

### 5a. Charger HealthcareService hs-ch-exemple-urgences (activité 157, mode 33)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/HealthcareService/hs-ch-exemple-urgences
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "HealthcareService",
  "id": "hs-ch-exemple-urgences",
  "providedBy": { "reference": "Organization/org-ch-exemple" },
  "specialty": [
    { "coding": [{ "code": "157", "system": "https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R211-ActiviteOperationnelle/FHIR/TRE-R211-ActiviteOperationnelle", "display": "Urgences polyvalentes hospitalières" }] }
  ],
  "characteristic": [
    { "coding": [{ "code": "33", "system": "https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R213-ModePriseEnCharge/FHIR/TRE-R213-ModePriseEnCharge", "display": "Accueil des urgences" }] }
  ]
}

### 5b. Charger HealthcareService hs-service-urgences-pediatriques (activité 249, mode 33)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/HealthcareService/hs-service-urgences-pediatriques
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "HealthcareService",
  "id": "hs-service-urgences-pediatriques",
  "providedBy": { "reference": "Organization/org-service-urgences" },
  "specialty": [
    { "coding": [{ "code": "249", "system": "https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R211-ActiviteOperationnelle/FHIR/TRE-R211-ActiviteOperationnelle", "display": "Urgences pédiatriques hospitalières" }] }
  ],
  "characteristic": [
    { "coding": [{ "code": "33", "system": "https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R213-ModePriseEnCharge/FHIR/TRE-R213-ModePriseEnCharge", "display": "Accueil des urgences" }] }
  ]
}

### 5c. Charger HealthcareService hs-clinique-exemple-urgences (activité 157, mode 33)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/HealthcareService/hs-clinique-exemple-urgences
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "HealthcareService",
  "id": "hs-clinique-exemple-urgences",
  "providedBy": { "reference": "Organization/org-clinique-exemple" },
  "specialty": [
    { "coding": [{ "code": "157", "system": "https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R211-ActiviteOperationnelle/FHIR/TRE-R211-ActiviteOperationnelle", "display": "Urgences polyvalentes hospitalières" }] }
  ],
  "characteristic": [
    { "coding": [{ "code": "33", "system": "https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R213-ModePriseEnCharge/FHIR/TRE-R213-ModePriseEnCharge", "display": "Accueil des urgences" }] }
  ]
}

### 6. $evaluate-measure SANS subject — reproduit "subjectCount: 0" et tous les compteurs à 0
POST {{baseUrl}}/Measure/OrganizationsNonConformesNomUrgence/$evaluate-measure
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Parameters",
  "parameter": [
    { "name": "periodStart", "valueDate": "2020-01-01" },
    { "name": "periodEnd", "valueDate": "2026-12-31" },
    { "name": "reportType", "valueCode": "subject-list" }
  ]
}

### 7. $evaluate-measure AVEC subject explicite (3 Organization présentes) — répond sans erreur mais compteurs à 0
POST {{baseUrl}}/Measure/OrganizationsNonConformesNomUrgence/$evaluate-measure
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Parameters",
  "parameter": [
    { "name": "periodStart", "valueDate": "2020-01-01" },
    { "name": "periodEnd", "valueDate": "2026-12-31" },
    { "name": "reportType", "valueCode": "subject" },
    { "name": "subject", "valueString": "Organization/org-ch-exemple" }
  ]
}

### 8. Library/$evaluate AVEC subject, 3 Organization présentes — reproduit l'erreur de cardinalité
### "Expected a list with at most one element, but found a list with multiple elements."
POST {{baseUrl}}/Library/OrganizationNomUrgence/$evaluate
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Parameters",
  "parameter": [
    { "name": "subject", "valueString": "Organization/org-ch-exemple" }
  ]
}

### 9a. Isoler une seule Organization — supprimer les HealthcareService liés aux 2 autres Organization
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/HealthcareService/hs-service-urgences-pediatriques

### 9b.
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/HealthcareService/hs-clinique-exemple-urgences

### 9c. Puis supprimer les 2 autres Organization (doit renvoyer 200, pas 409, une fois les HS supprimés)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/Organization/org-service-urgences

### 9d.
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/Organization/org-clinique-exemple

### 10. Rejouer Library/$evaluate — avec 1 seule Organization sur le serveur, ça fonctionne (résultat attendu ci-dessous)
### InitialPopulation=true, Denominator=true, NomContientUrgence=false, Numerator=true
POST {{baseUrl}}/Library/OrganizationNomUrgence/$evaluate
Content-Type: application/fhir+json

{
  "resourceType": "Parameters",
  "parameter": [
    { "name": "subject", "valueString": "Organization/org-ch-exemple" }
  ]
}

